Title: Part 11: The Road to Mordor
Text:
Fighting through Osgiliath wasn't easy!

Orcs swarmed the East bank...

I'm afraid I have to hurry..
Somewhere to the east there must be a road leading into the Old Morgul Valley...

...not the safest way... but I have no alternative!
CompleteText:
I found it! the Morgul Valley!

The ancient city of Minas Ithil once belonged to Gondor before the Witch-king of Angmar conquered it...

According to Gollum, there is a secret stairway to Mordor in these mountains!
Can I trust him?...
